      <article class="prose-shopify mt-14 max-w-4xl">
        <p>Klaviyo vs Yotpo Email & SMS: scenario 1 — subscription toggle left on at checkout. At $253 AOV and 34% margin, full-price recovery contributes $86.02 vs $73.98 after a 14% code (Δ $12.04). Ladder touch 1 favors push nudge; watch for duplicate SMS and email within 20 minutes. Email 1 ~114m, email 2 ~34h, SMS branch ~3h for opted-in only.</p>
